OL,4,Crelationship with domestic abuse victim
OL,6,FA police officer from Yeovil has been
OL,7,Fbarred due to pursuing a relationship
OL,8,Fwith a domestic abuse survivor.
OL,10,FThe officer, referred to as PC Z and
OL,11,Fbased in Yeovil, cannot be named for
OL,12,Flegal reasons. He joined the force in
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FHe first met the woman, Miss A, during
OL,16,Fan investigation he was involved in.
