OL,3,CYeovil police officer tried to have
OL,4,Crelationship with domestic abuse victim
OL,6,FBetween November 2022 and February
OL,7,F2023, the officer contacted her 69
OL,8,Ftimes on nine different dates by text
OL,9,Fmessage and phone calls. There was no
OL,10,Fobvious record of this contact on
OL,11,Fpolice records.
OL,13,FBarrister Mark Ley-Morgan,
OL,14,Frepresenting the force, said: "In
OL,15,FNovember 2022, he met Miss A who told
OL,16,Fhim there had been domestic incidents
OL,17,Fbetween her and her partner, so he was
OL,18,Faware she was vulnerable.
