OL,4,Crelationship with domestic abuse victim
OL,6,F"Between November 2022 and February
OL,7,F2023 he pursued an emotional
OL,8,Frelationship with Miss A.
OL,10,F"He exchanged numerous text messages,
OL,11,Fhad phone conversations and visited
OL,12,Fher home without a policing purpose.
OL,14,F"He told Miss A that he should not be
OL,15,Fmessaging her as he had met her
OL,16,Fthrough his police duties and asked
OL,17,Fher to delete the messages."
