OL,3,CYeovil police officer tried to have
OL,4,Crelationship with domestic abuse victim
OL,6,FMr Ley-Morgan said the response
OL,7,Fofficer was told in May 2023 by the
OL,8,Fforce's professional standards
OL,9,Fdepartment that he was under
OL,10,Finvestigation and was required to meet
OL,11,Fthem in person to be issued with a
OL,12,Fnotice.
OL,14,FBefore he did this, PC Z deleted the
OL,15,Fmessages from his work mobile phone.
OL,17,FMr Ley-Morgan said: "He covered up or
OL,18,Fattempted to cover up his contact by
OL,19,Fasking her to delete the messages and
OL,20,Fdeleting them from his phone.
OL,26,@yD@UOU
