OL,3,CYeovil police officer tried to have
OL,4,Crelationship with domestic abuse victim
OL,6,FHe said: "He knew what he was doing
OL,7,Fwas wrong. He tried to get Miss A to
OL,8,Fdelete messages. Then, when he
OL,9,Frealised he was under investigation,
OL,10,Fhe deleted his messages.
OL,12,F"He was concealing it."
OL,14,FMr Ley-Morgan said the constable
OL,15,Fpursued an emotional, although not
OL,16,Fsexual, relationship with the woman.
OL,18,FThe officer's Police Federation rep
OL,19,FAndrew Coggins said PC Z apologised
OL,20,Ffor any distress caused to the woman
OL,21,Fand embarrassment to the force.
