OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said the ex-
OL,7,Fconstable was granted anonymity by the
OL,8,Fpanel chair because of a concern
OL,9,Fregarding the risk of harm to
OL,10,Fwitnesses if the officer's identity
OL,11,Fwas made public.
OL,13,FAfterwards, head of the professional
OL,14,Fstandards department Detective
OL,15,FSuperintendent Larisa Hunt said:
OL,16,F"Following contact from a member of
OL,17,Fthe public in March 2023, a full
OL,18,Finvestigation was launched into the
OL,19,Falleged actions of PC Z.
