OL,4,Crelationship with domestic abuse victim
OL,6,F"This incident was initially referred
OL,7,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct which deemed it appropriate
OL,9,Ffor local investigation.
OL,11,F"When investigating PC Z's phone
OL,12,Frecords, several texts and calls to
OL,13,Fthe woman were discovered and, in some
OL,14,Finstances, the contents of the texts
OL,15,Fwere recovered.
OL,17,F"The records showed that PC Z had
OL,18,Fcontacted her both on-duty and on his
OL,19,Frest days and several texts had been
OL,20,Fdeleted.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
