OL,6,F"He abused his position of power as a
OL,7,Fpolice officer, and his behaviour
OL,8,Ftowards a vulnerable member of our
OL,9,Fsociety is unacceptable.
OL,11,F"We are grateful to the individual who
OL,12,Fhad the confidence to report this to
OL,13,Fus and allow us to carry out a full
OL,14,Finvestigation and ensure PC Z will
OL,15,Fnever serve in policing again.
OL,17,F"We hope today's outcome encourages
OL,18,Fother people to have trust in policing
OL,19,Fand the confidence to report
OL,20,Finappropriate behaviour to us in the
OL,21,Ffuture."
